1.0.name: wordpress/jquery-accessible-button
1.0.description: JQuery Accessible Button is button group controling the number of your blog's recent posts, recent comments and archives shown in an accordion and uses the JQuery WAI-ARIA enabled accordion and button. Use it in a wide widget area, like the "First Footer Widget Area".
